    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This should be handled by some custom templates, but we need to find a way to define several templates for one element.\n\nMaybe the `template` key for this widget could be an object like this:\n\n``` javascript\n{\n  first: '<a href=\"{{url}}\"><i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i></a>',\n  previous: '...',\n  page: '<a href=\"{{url}}\">{{page}}</a>',\n  next: '...',\n  last: '...'\n}\n```\n",
